%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindus%20Haven't%20'Lost'%20Their%20Way%3A%20Unveiling%20the%20'Pseudo-Religiosity'%20Behind%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20Campaign%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22185025%2FScreenshot-2024-01-22-at-12.41.27-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAre%20Hindus%20in%20need%20of%20a%20spiritual%2C%20cultural%2C%20religious%20reawakening%3F%20Have%20India%E2%80%99s%20over%20120%20crore%20Hindus%20%E2%80%98lost%20their%20way%E2%80%99%3F%20And%2C%20is%20the%20new%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20the%20only%20way%20to%20save%20their%20souls%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%20lakhs%20of%20Indians%20visit%20the%20Balaji%20temple%20at%20Tirupati.%20Lakhs%20trek%20up%20to%20Vaishno%20Devi%20temple%20near%20Jammu.%20Lakhs%20flock%20to%20Guwahati%E2%80%99s%20famous%20Kamakhya%20temple%2C%20to%20the%20Jagannath%20temple%20in%20Puri%2C%20to%20the%20Vithoba%20temple%20in%20Pandharpur.%20There%20are%2C%20literally%2C%20thousands%20of%20temples%20across%20India%20%E2%80%93%20big%2C%20small%2C%20ancient%2C%20recent%20%E2%80%93%20dedicated%20to%20scores%20of%20Indian%20gods%20and%20goddesses%2C%20and%20crores%20of%20devout%20Hindus%20go%20to%20these%20temples%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20the%20crores%20of%20Hindus%20who%20have%20allegedly%20lost%20their%20way%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrores%20of%20Hindu%20shopkeepers%20dedicate%20a%20little%20alcove%20to%20their%20preferred%20deity%20even%20in%20the%20tiniest%20of%20shops%2C%20and%20the%20day%E2%80%99s%20work%20begins%20with%20a%20prayer%20and%20the%20ritual%20tinkling%20of%20a%20bell.%20Crores%20of%20Hindus%20have%20%E2%80%98mandirs%E2%80%99%20in%20their%20homes%20%E2%80%93%20some%20modest%2C%20some%20grand%20%E2%80%93%20and%20there%20too%2C%20the%20average%20Hindu%20family%20performs%20regular%20%E2%80%98aarti%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98puja%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20the%20Hindus%20who%20have%20lost%20touch%20with%20their%20religion%3F%20No.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESorry%2C%20Hindus%20have%20not%20%E2%80%98lost%E2%80%99%20their%20way%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrores%20of%20Hindus%20follow%20the%20rituals%20laid%20down%20for%20key%20moments%20of%20a%20Hindu%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20such%20as%20the%20birth%20and%20naming%20of%20a%20child%2C%20marriage%2C%20the%20entry%20into%20a%20new%20home%2C%20and%20death%2C%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20not%20practising%2C%20god-fearing%20Hindus%3F%20Yes%2C%20they%20most%20certainly%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20then%2C%20where%20are%20the%20%E2%80%98lost%E2%80%99%20Hindus%20that%20need%20%E2%80%98re-awakening%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98de-colonising%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20has%20been%20a%20well-executed%2C%20well-milked%20political%20project.%20The%20idea%20being%20to%20harvest%20votes%20from%20a%20sense%20of%20%E2%80%98resurgent%E2%80%99%20Hindu%20pride%2C%20derived%20from%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20grand%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20allowing%20all%20the%20credit%20to%20accrue%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20hoping%20it%20translates%20into%20a%20win%20in%20the%20General%20Election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20problem%20is%2C%20the%20whole%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fbooks%2Fessay-media-religious-conversion%5C%22%3Enarrative%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fwhy-its-crucial-to-understand-that-hindu-pride-goes-beyond-the-modi-factor%5C%22%3Eof%20%E2%80%98lost%E2%80%99%20Hindus%20and%20%E2%80%98hurt%E2%80%99%20pride%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20false%20construct.%20Simply%20put%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Hindus%20are%20neither%20%E2%80%98lost%E2%80%99%20nor%20%E2%80%98hurt%E2%80%99.%20Their%20pride%20and%20their%20faith%20is%20pretty%20intact%20too.%20Every%20political%20party%20and%20its%20ideologues%20and%20its%20intellectual%20supporters%20may%20put%20a%20%E2%80%98deeper%E2%80%99%20spin%20on%20any%20political%20gimmick%20they%20roll%20out.%20But%20they%20should%20not%20start%20believing%20their%20own%20spin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERam%20Mandir%20hype%20is%20%E2%80%98pseudo-religosity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%2C%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20were%20accused%20of%20practising%20%E2%80%98minority-appeasement%E2%80%99%20politics%20and%20labelled%20%E2%80%98pseudo-secular.%E2%80%99%20Today%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98majority%20appeasement%E2%80%99%20that%20has%20culminated%20in%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20accompanied%20by%20hyped-up%20%E2%80%98pseudo-religiosity%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98pseudo-spiritual-reawakening%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20devout%20are%20welcome%20to%20jet%20into%20Ayodhya%2C%20stay%20at%20a%20swanky%20hotel%2C%20and%20get%20a%20%E2%80%98darshan%E2%80%99%20at%20the%20grand%20mandir.%20But%20just%20as%20intrinsically%20Hindu%20is%20the%20long%20trek%20to%20the%20Amarnath%20cave%20or%20Kedarnath%20or%20Gangotri%20Dham%2C%20or%20to%20the%20Vaishno%20Devi%20mandir%2C%20and%20then%20getting%20darshan%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98deity%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20arduous%20nature%20of%20the%20journey%20that%20makes%20it%20a%20test%20of%20the%20pilgrim%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98faith%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20crores%20of%20Indians%20have%20been%20passing%20this%20test%20for%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20may%20well%20add%20the%20new%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Mandir%20to%20their%20bucket%20list%2C%20but%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20make%20them%20any%20more%20Hindu%2C%20or%20any%20more%20aware%20of%20their%20Hindu%20identity%2C%20than%20they%20already%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-conten