f425fdd23d01c201edb40c0cd414f3c8d1ff701fbf8a20f7465b%26postID%3D65bcb18c178f29663aab5e86%26postSlug%3Dstarbucks-gopuff-late-night-deliveries-coffee-food-drinks-philadelphia-pennsylvania-2024-2%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.gopuff.com%252Fnewsroom%252Fcompany-news%252Fgopuff-now-delivering-starbucks-from-philadelphia-mfcs-in-new-pilot-program%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20October%20which%20said%20that%20the%20two%20companies%20were%20starting%20food%20and%20beverage%20deliveries%20in%20Philadelphia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20press%20release%20said%20that%20the%20orders%20would%20be%20prepared%20by%20Starbucks-trained%20baristas%20employed%20by%20Gopuff%2C%20operating%20from%20two%20of%20Gopuff's%20Philadelphia%20micro-fulfillment%20centers.%20Customers%20would%20be%20able%20to%20order%20other%20non-Starbucks%20items%20as%20part%20of%20the%20same%20delivery%2C%20the%20companies%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Philadelphia%20Inquirer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inquirer.com%2Fbusiness%2Fgopuff-delivery-starbucks-coffee-philly-20231004.html%23loaded%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20micro-fulfillment%20centers%20in%20the%20city%20offered%2024-hour%20delivery%20from%20the%20start.%20Around%20three%20dozen%20employees%20were%20trained%20to%20prepare%20Starbucks%20orders%20at%20the%20two%20sites%2C%20it%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Business%20Insider%20looked%20at%20around%204%3A30%20a.m.%20local%20time%2C%20Starbucks%20items%20available%20to%20order%20via%20Gopuff%20in%20Philadelphia%20included%20Frappuccinos%2C%20iced%20coffees%2C%20lattes%2C%20bakery%20items%2C%20sandwiches%2C%20and%20hot%20food.%20Many%20of%20the%20items%20were%20discounted%2C%20like%20avocado%20spread%20reduced%20from%20%241.25%20to%20%240.25.%20All%20the%20bakery%20items%20were%20at%20least%2025%25%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222184%5C%