20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20fancied%20living%20in%20another%20country%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20have%20anywhere%20particular%20in%20mind.%20I%20am%20originally%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20North%20Wales.%20Before%20arriving%20in%20Japan%20in%202007%2C%20I%20studied%20medieval%20history%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Manchester.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20university%2C%20I%20heard%20about%20programs%20for%20people%20to%20teach%20English%20in%20Japan%2C%20somewhere%20I'd%20only%20seen%20in%20video%20games%20and%20on%20television.%20What%20I%20thought%20would%20be%20a%20one%20or%20two-year%20adventure%20completely%20altered%20the%20course%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Osaka%20and%20worked%20as%20an%20assistant%20English%20teacher%20in%20the%20suburbs.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20I%20gradually%20started%20to%20do%20more%20freelance%20writing%20work%2C%20mainly%20related%20to%20travel%20and%20the%20outdoors.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20primarily%20a%20freelance%20writer%20and%20copywriter%2C%20although%20I%20still%20do%20some%20teaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202022%2C%20I%20have%20lived%20in%20a%20renovated%20150-year-old%20farmhouse%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20southern%20Kyoto.%20I've%20always%20been%20more%20comfortable%20living%20in%20a%20rural%20setting%2C%20and%2C%20after%2015%20years%20in%20Osaka%2C%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20say%20goodbye%20to%20city%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20spent%20years%20looking%20for%20an%20old%20house%20with%20some%20land%20and%20eventually%20found%20the%20perfect%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20thing%20is%20its%20location%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20only%20an%20hour%20by%20train%20to%20Osaka%20or%20Kyoto%2C%20yet%20it%20feels%20like%20another%20world.%20The%20house%20backs%20onto%20a%20mountain.%20Monkeys%2C%20wild%20boar%20and%20deer%20visit%20my%20garden.%20I%20have%20space%20for%20farming%20and%20BBQs%2C%20and%20the%20neighbors%20are%20lovely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20negatives%20are%20that%20it%20costs%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20refurbish%20an%20old%20house%20in%20Japan%2C%20even%20though%20the%20initial%20cost%20of%20buying%20was%20cheap.%20Summers%20are%20also%20hot%20and%20humid%2C%20although%20the%20countryside%20is%20noticeably%20cooler%20than%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan%20is%20a%20great%20place%20to%20live%20as%20a%20foreigner.%20I%20love%20the%20food%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20crime%20compared%20to%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20feeling%20safe%20in%20general.%20I%20enjoy%20Japan's%20varied%20natural%20landscapes%2C%20excellent%20public%20transport%2C%20and%20people's%20kindness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConversely%2C%20you%20will%20always%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20outsider%20in%20Japan.%20Aside%20from%20general%20language%20challenges%2C%20there%20are%20sometimes%20infuriating%20levels%20of%20bureaucracy.%20If%20you%20can%20handle%20those%20things%2C%20it's%20an%20easy%20and%20comfortable%20place%20to%20live.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20I've%20found%20a%20few%20surprising%20things%20living%20in%20Japan%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGood%20quality%20cheese%20and%20Western%20products%20are%20hard%20to%20come%20by%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20should%20have%20brought%20more%20cheese%20with%20me%2C%20as%20it%20is%20very%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20as%20good%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Japan.%20I%20also%20struggle%20to%20find%20effective%20Japanese%20deodorant%20or%20toothpaste%3B%C2%A0the%20options%20here%20are%20often%20too%20weak.%20I%20either%20go%20without%20or%20occasionally%20get%20packages%20sent%20from%20home%20or%20stock%20up%20when%20I%20visit%20the%20UK.%20Living%20in%20Japan%20has%20broadened%20my%20palette%20for%20seafood%20and%20local%20seasonal%20vegetables%2C%20which%20are%20readily%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPeople%20don't%20speak%20a%20lot%20of%20English%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20prevalence%20of%20Western%20culture%20and%20a%20push%20to%20teach%20English%20in%20schools%2C%20the%20general%20English%20ability%20is%20low%20at%20best%2C%20so%20any%20Japanese%20you%20can%20learn%20in%20advance%20makes%20moving%20here%20much%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20weather%20varies%20massively%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESummers%20are%20incredibly%20hot%2C%20and%20winters%20are%20incredibly%20cold%20throughout%20most%20of%20Japan.%20Be%20prepared%20for%20extreme%20changes%20in%20weather.%20It%20may%20also%20help%20to%20research%20the%20region%20you%20will%20live%20in%2C%20as%20localities%20differ%20greatly%20in%20snowfall%2C%20typhoons%2C%20and%20tsunami%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EJapan%20is%20not%20as%20high-tech%20as%20most%20people%20imagine%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20still%20use%20fax%20machines%2C%20sometimes%20you%20have%20to%20print%20out%20emails%2C%20and%20many%20government%20offices%20have%20barely%20changed%20since%20the%201980s.%20The%20low-tech%20approach%20means%20things%20are%20not%20as%20efficient%20as%20most%20people%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20cause%20me%20trouble%2C%20but%20I%20can%20see%20how%20some%20people%20become%20infuriated.%20There%20are%20also%20multiple%20levels%20of%20bureaucracy%20and%20rules%20to%20get%20official%20things%20done%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0patience%20and%20persistence%20are%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECity%20living%20and%20countryside%20living%20are%20very%20different%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20I'd%20moved%20to%20the%20countryside%20even%20sooner.%20My%20monthly%20mortgage%20repayment%20is%20way%20less%20than%20my%20city%20rent%20and%20my%20quality%20of%20life%20is%20exponentially%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECountryside%20life%20is%20much%20quieter.%20Our%20neighbors%20are%20friendly%20and%20give%20us%20vegetables%20and%20food%20from%20their%20fields.%20Being%20surrounded%20by%20interesting%20wildlife%20and%20the%20changing%20seasons%20never%20gets%20boring.%20The%20air%20is%20fresher%2C%20and%20summers%20are%20cooler%20than%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELearning%20Japanese%20history%20can%20enrich%20your%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELearning%20about%20the%20origins%20of%20a%20particular%20shrine%20or%20tradition%20%E2%80%94%20the%20%26quot%3BObon%26quot%3B%20holiday%20or%20the%20New%20Year%20%26quot%3Bsh%3Cspan%3E%C5%8D%3C%2Fspan%3Egatsu%26quot%3B%20festivities%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%94%20adds%20an%20extra%20level%20of%20richness%20to%20daily%20life%20and%20explains%20some%20customs%20Westerners%20might%20find%20unusual.%20Food%20in%20Japan%20is%20also%20intrinsically%20linked%20to%20history%2C%20often%20in%20the%20way%20it%20has%20developed%2C%20is%20eaten%2C%20or%20presented.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20basic%20level%20of%20knowledge%20will%20help%20you%20better%20understand%20Japan%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20infrastructure%2C%20society%2C%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EJapan%20is%20a%20great%20place%20to%20dive%20into%20your%20hobbies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20seen%20all%20the%20big%20touristy%20sights%20and%20places%2C%20spend%20your%20time%20digging%20deep%20into%20things%20that%20interest%20you.%20For%20example%2C%20I'm%20really%20into%20hiking.%20If%20you%20go%20hiking%20in%20Japan%2C%20even%20on%20short%20nature%20trails%2C%20everyone%20is%20kitted%20out%20in%20all%20the%20gear%20as%20if%20they're%20pioneering%20a%20new%20route%20in%20the%20Himalayas.%20That%20is%20the%20way%20in%20Japan%3A%20people%20go%20full-in%20and%20full-on%2C%20and%20it%20is%20not%20ridiculed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20applies%20to%20people%20with%20far%20more%20niche%20interests%2C%20such%20as%20obscure%20manga%20or%20bonsai%20gardening.%20This%20is%20a%20great%20place%20to%20get%20geeky%20about%20things.%20People%20are%20not%20judgmental%2C%20and%20finding%20people%20who%20enjoy%20your%20passion%20is%20a%20good%20way%20to%20make%20friends%2C%20especially%20as%20culturally%20Japanese%20people%20are%20more%20reserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20see%20myself%20living%20in%20Japan%20forever%2C%20but%20part%20of%20me%20would%20like%20to%