Cli%3EBorrowers%20not%20enrolled%20in%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20will%20need%20to%20do%20so%20to%20make%20use%20of%20the%20benefit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20student-loan%20borrowers%20can%20expect%20debt%20relief%20starting%20this%20month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-student-loan-forgiveness-early-income-driven-repayment-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethrough%20a%20new%20repayment%20reform%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%20January%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20announced%20that%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20the%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%20who%20originally%20borrowed%20%2412%2C000%20or%20less%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-debt-relief-loan-forgiveness-coming-quickly-certain-borrowers-biden-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewill%20begin%20to%20see%20their%20loans%20forgiven%20in%20February%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20making%20as%20few%20as%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20is%20rolling%20out%20this%20relief%20early%20%E2%80%94%20when%20SAVE%20was%20first%20announced%20over%20the%20summer%2C%20that%20provision%20of%20the%20plan%20wasn't%20set%20to%20be%20implemented%20until%20the%20summer%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiving%20borrowers%20with%20smaller%20loans%20a%20faster%20path%20to%20being%20debt%20free%20will%20help%20many%20borrowers%20avoid%20financial%20distress%20and%20have%20peace%20of%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20Education%20James%20Kvaal%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20how%20many%20borrowers%20will%20immediately%20qualify%20for%20relief%2C%20and%20when%20those%20notices%20will%20start%20being%20sent%20out%20this%20month.%20Additionally%2C%20borrowers%20who%20are%20not%20currently%20enrolled%20in%20the%20SAVE%20plan%20will%20need%20to%20enroll%20at%20studentaid.gov%20in%20order%20to%20qualify%20for%20this%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E