Vote%20to%20Oust%20Founder%20Raveendran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F15190825%2Fimage-652.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20consortium%20of%20key%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20shareholders%2C%20collectively%20holding%20a%20stake%20of%20over%2030%25%20in%20the%20ed-tech%20company%2C%20has%20called%20for%20an%20extraordinary%20general%20meeting%20(EGM)%20with%20the%20objective%20of%20ousting%20Byju%20Raveendran%20and%20his%20family%20members%20from%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cthird%20time%20the%20investors%20are%20issuing%20an%20EGM%20notice.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20rights%20to%20enforce%20an%20EGM%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20person%20close%20to%20the%20developments%20told%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology%2Fbyjus-investors-issue-egm-notice-for-reconstitution-of-board-say-deeply-concerned-about-future-stability-under-current-leadership-12174591.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20moneycontrol.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EGM%20is%20being%20called%20to%20reconstitute%20the%20board%20of%20directors%2C%20so%20that%20it%20is%20no%20longer%20controlled%20by%20the%20founders%20of%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20parent%20company%2C%20Think%20%26amp%3B%20Learn%20(T%26amp%3BL)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftech%2Fstartups%2Fbyjus-shareholder-group-calls-for-egm-to-vote-for-ouster-of-byju-raveendran-board%2Farticleshow%2F107326462.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20released%20on%20February%201%20(Thursday)%2C%20the%20shareholders%20said%20that%20such%20notices%20of%20requisition%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20T%26amp%3BL%20board%20of%20directors%20in%20July%20and%20December%202023%20as%20well%2C%20which%20were%20disregarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investors%20want%20to%20address%20governance%20concerns%2C%20financial%20mismanagement%20and%20compliance%20issues%20at%20the%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EThese%20shareholders%20include%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20Prosus%2C%20Peak%20XV%20Partners%20(formerly%20Sequoia%20Capital)%2C%20General%20Atlantic%2C%20Sofina%2C%20The%20Chan%20Zuckerberg%20Initiative%2C%20Owl%20Ventures%20and%20Sand%20Capital.%20And%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20instance%20these%20shareholders%20have%20come%20together%20to%20seek%20a%20change%20of%20guard%20in%20the%20company%2C%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fcharting-the-rise-and-fall-of-byjus-and-educational-ecosystem-in-india%5C%22%3ECharting%20the%20Rise%20and%20Fall%20of%20Byju%E2%80%99s%2C%20a%20New%20Book%20Explores%20India%E2%80%99s%20Educational%20Ecosystem%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EThis%20comes%20days%20after%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fout-with-the-board-say-angry-byjus-investors-11706809657292.html%5C%22%3Elaunched%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20rights%20issue%20to%20raise%20%24200%20million%20from%20existing%20shareholders.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20rights%20issue%20is%20a%20way%20for%20a%20company%20to%20raise%20capital%20by%20offering%20existing%20shareholders%20the%20opportunity%20to%20buy%20additional%20shares%20at%20a%20discounted%20price%2C%20typically%20in%20proportion%20to%20their%20existing%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju%E2%80%99s%20rights%20issue%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20priced%20at%20a%2099%25%20cut%20to%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20previous%20peak%20valuation%20of%20%2422%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20such%20a%20low%20price%2C%20if%20existing%20shareholders%20do%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20rights%20issue%2C%20they%20will%20see%20their%20ownership%20stake%20in%20the%20company%20diluted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20investors%20like%20Prosus%20and%20Peak%20XV%20need%20to%20pump%20in%20%2418%20million%20and%20%2414%20million%2C%20respectively%2C%20or%20they%20will%20virtually%20see%20their%20holding%20wiped%20off%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftech%2Fstartups%2Fbyjus-shareholder-group-calls-for-egm-to-vote-for-ouster-of-byju-raveendran-board%2Farticleshow%2F107326462.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20EGM%2C%20the%20shareholders%20will%20vote%20to%20oust%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20CEO%20Raveendran%20and%20his%20family%20members%20from%20the%20board%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20restrain%20them%20from%20running%20the%20operations%20at%20the%20edtech%20startup%2C%20people%20in%20the%20know%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20and%20family%20own%20about%2026%25%20in%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20future%20stability%20of%20the%20company%20under%20its%20current%20leadership%20and%20with%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20investors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20resolution%20to%20pass%20at%20the%20EGM%2C%20it%20will%20need%20to%20muster%20support%20of%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20cited%20above%20said%20the%20investors%20are%20planning%20to%20have%20a%20new%20management%20and%20board%20at%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20to%20steer%20the%20company%20forward%20if%20they%20win%20the%20required%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20missing%20multiple%20deadlines%2C%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20finally%20submitted%20its%20financial%20statements%20for%20fiscal%20year%202022.%20The%20edtech%20giant%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fbyjus-incurs-over-rs-8000-crore-in-losses-in-fy22-driven-by-whitehat-jr-and-osmo%5C%22%3E%20losses%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20doubled%20to%20Rs%208%2C245%