ch%20several%20people%20recounted%20what%20it%20was%20like%20being%20in%20prison%20with%20Stewart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20Stewart%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.cnn.com%2F2004%2F03%2F05%2Fnews%2Fcompanies%2Fmartha_verdict%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20guilty%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20charges%20including%20conspiracy%2C%20making%20false%20statements%2C%20and%20obstruction%20of%20justice%20related%20to%20the%20sale%20of%20stocks.%20She%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.loc.gov%2Fexhibitions%2Fdrawing-justice-courtroom-illustrations%2Fabout-this-exhibition%2Fcelebrity-trials%2Fmartha-stewart-on-trial-for-insider-trading%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserved%3C%2Fa%3E%20five%20months%20in%20Federal%20Prison%20Camp%20Alderson%20in%20West%20Virginia%20and%20another%20two%20years%20of%20supervised%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20CNN%20series%2C%20Meg%20Phipps%2C%20who%20was%20incarcerated%20at%20the%20same%20time%20and%20in%20the%20same%20prison%20as%20Stewart%2C%20said%20she%20once%20received%20a%20sweet%20treat%20from%20the%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20received%20a%20note%20from%20Martha.%20She%20suggested%20that%20we%20meet%2C%26quot%3B%20Phipps%20said%20in%20the%20clip.%20%26quot%3BShe%20also%20sent%20that%20note%20with%20a%20baked%20apple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20baked%20apple%20%26quot%3Bhad%20caramel%20on%20it%20and%20probably%20some%20cinnamon%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20Stewart%20had%20found%20a%20way%20to%20cook%20in%20her%20room%20using%20the%20microwave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20suspect%20some%20of%20this%20may%20have%20come%20from%20the%20cafeteria%2C%20which%20we're%20not%20supposed%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Phipps%20said%20of%20the%20ingredients%20in%20the%20treat%2C%20per%20the%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhipps%20also%20said%20in%20the%20miniseries%20that%20everyone%20held%20a%20potluck%20to%20celebrate%20Stewart's%20release%20on%20the%20day%20she%20left%20prison%2C%20per%20People.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20brought%20different%20dishes%2C%20but%20Martha%20did%20bring%20a%20caramel%20flan%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20she%20made%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Phipps%20said%2C%20per%20People.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20big%20part%20about%20what%20made%20prison%20tolerable%20is%20that%20fellowship%20of%20cooking%20and%20celebrating%20someone%20going%20home.%20She%20thanked%20people%20for%20making%20her%20time%20there%20go%20as%20well%20as%20it%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20two%20episodes%20of%20the%20four-part%20series%20premiered%20on%20January%2028%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcnncreativemarketing.com%2Fproject%2Fthe-many-lives-of-martha-stewart%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20last%20two%20episodes%20are%20slated%20to%20be%20released%20on%20February%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202016%2C%20Stewart%20said%20at%20the%20Cannes%20Lion%20Festival%20that%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartha-stewart-daily-mail-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espent%20her%20time%20in%20prison%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20jam%20out%20of%20the%20crab%20apples%20on%20the%20trees%26quot%3B%20and%20attending%20ceramics%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20even%20able%20to%20send%20the%20ceramics%20home%2C%20she%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20to%20beg%20and%20borrow%20bubble%20wrap%20and%20boxes%20and%20things.%20I%20sent%20it%20all%20home%20and%20it%20arrived.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Snoop%20Dogg%20told%20BI%20that%20Stewart%20learned%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnoop-dogg-martha-stewart-favorite-dishes-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efried%20chicken%20recipe%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20now%20one%20of%20his%20favorites%20%E2%80%94%20while%20she%20was%20behind%20bars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20told%20me%20that%20one%20of%20the%20homegirls%20gave%20her%20some%20sort%20of%20recipe%20that%20when%20she%20got%20out%20she%20used%2C%20and%20it%20was%20effective%2C%20and%20it%20was%20dope%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20rapper%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20meet%20some%20talented%20people%20behind%20the%20wall%2C%20you%20gotta%20know%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Stewart%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartha-stewart-baked-desserts-in-prison-former-fellow-inmates-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706861851000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bc4fe543bb77284ba2ddad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartha-stewart-baked-desserts-in-prison-former-fellow-inmates-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20inmates%20who%20knew%20Martha%20Stewart%20from%20their%20time%20in%20prison%20spoke%20about%20the%20star%20in%20a%20new%20CNN%20miniseries%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Many%20Lives%20of%20Martha%20Stewart.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A46%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmartha-stewart-baked-desserts-in-prison-former-fellow-inmates-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Must%20Forge%20Ahead%2C%20Leaving%20Nitish%20Kumar%20Behind%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F18155503%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-18-at-1.20.10-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20another%20episode%20of%20unscrupulous%20trickery%20has%20materialised%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20general%20who%20had%20been%20gathering%20forces%20ostensibly%20to%20save%20the%20realm%20has%2C%20Coriolanus-like%2C%20thought%20it%20best%20(not%20for%20the%20first%20time)%20to%20go%20join%20the%20enemy.%20This%20latest%20coup%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20Houdini%20is%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20undertaken%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20interest%E2%80%9D%3B%20once%20more%2C%20it%20underscores%20the%20truth%C2%A0%20of%C2%A0%20that%20high-minded%20claim%20sung%20in%20the%20movie%20%3Cem%3EJish%20Desh%20Mei%20Ganga%20Behti%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHontoun%20pe%20sacchai%20rehti%20hai%2F%20Yehan%20dil%20mei%20safai%20rehti%20hai%2F%20Hum%20uss%20desh%20ke%20vaasi%20hein%2F%20Jish%20desh%20mei%20Ganga%20behi%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Truth%20on%20our%20lips%2C%20purity%20in%20our%20heart%2F%20We%20are%20the%20people%20of%20the%20land%2F%20Blessed%20by%20the%20flow%20of%20the%20River%20Ganga).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20corollary%20to%20the%20new%20Nitish-antic%20is%20that%20the%20media%2C%20by%20and%20large%2C%20feels%20less%20reviled%20by%20this%20unprincipled%20shift%20and%20is%20more%20outraged%20by%20the%20greediness%C2%A0%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20not%20having%20risen%20in%20time%20to%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20selflessly%20Herculean%20determination%20to%20oust%20the%20ruling%20right-wing%20from%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYou%20see%2C%20if%20the%20corporate-chummy%20%E2%80%9Cnationalist%E2%80%9D%20ruling%20party%20is%20to%20be%20kept%20in%20the%20saddle%2C%20the%20media%20must%20never%20cease%20to%20find%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20wrong%2C%C2%A0%20whatever%20journalistic%C2%A0%20calisthenics%C2%A0%20the%20job%20may%20entail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20poor%20Trump%20has%20but%20one%20Fox%20News%20backing%20him%2C%20our%20greater%20Modi%20ji%20has%20a%20bevy%20of%20them%2C%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhich%20is%20not%20to%20say%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20not%20often%20blameworthy%20for%20being%20out%20of%20sync%20with%20the%20content%20and%20pace%20of%20moves%20on%20the%20political%20chessboard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20plain%20truth%20of%20the%20matter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20that%20in%20Bharat%20the%20appellation%20%E2%80%9Ccorrupt%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20applies%C2%A0%20only%20to%20financial%20sleaziness%2C%20never%20to%20unethical%20political%C2%A0%20practices%20(smartly%20duplicitous%20leaders%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20are%20often%20lauded%20for%20being%20the%20true%20inheritors%20of%20Chanakya)%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20having%20had%20enough%20of%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20ministership%2C%20had%20India%E2%80%99s%20prime%20ministership%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20to%20happen%2C%20he%20had%20to%20have%20a%20new%20political%20conglomeration%20foregrounding%20his%20selfless%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20elevation%2C%20by%20common%20consent%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cchairperson%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20brought%20bad%20news%20to%20Nishit%20Kumar%20in%20that%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20best%20thing%2C%20therefore%2C%20to%20the%20prospect%20of%20seeing%C2%A0%20an%20alternative%20government%20with%20Kharge%20and%20the%20Congress%20at%20the%C2%A0%20helm%C2%A0%20was%20to%20make%20as%20sure%20as%20possible%C2%A0%20that%20the%C2%A0%20current%20dispensation%20carried%20on%20with%20him%20in%20the%20familiar%20chief%20minster%E2%80%99s%20chair%20after%20taking%20yet%20another%20principled%2C%20oath%20of%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20wit%2C%20bird%20in%20hand%20is%20always%20better%20than%20two%20in%20the%20bush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20may%20be%20blamed%20for%20having%20speculated%20that%20the%20next%20Nitish%20somersault%20may%20well%20happen%20if%20and%20when%20an%20alternate%20INDIA%20government%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20record%2C%20what%20is%20there%20to%20say%20this%20could%20not%20have%20happened%2C%20given%C2%A0%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20never-ending%20creativity%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENor%20might%20the%20Congress%20have%20been%20the%20only%20component%20of%20the%20alliance%20to%20have%20such%20tribulations%20on%20their%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetter%2C%20therefore%2C%20that%20Kumar%20was%20given%20full%20play%20to%20reach%20his%C2%A0%20conclusions%20than%20be%20sorry%20afterwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%20that%20the%20deed%20is%20done%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20and%20other%20federal%C2%A0%20leaders%20of%20the%20alliance%20will%20never%20be%20applauded%20by%20the%20current%20slew%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20upright%20media%20for%20having%20stood%20their%20ground%20against%20right-wing%20sectarian%20ideology%2C%20as%20we%20know%2C%20at%20great%20cost%20to%20themselves%20and%20their%20political%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20truly%20their%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20ever-swinging%20JD(U)%20out%20%E2%80%93%20noting%20that%20many%20of%20its%20members%20are%20as%20unhappy%20with%20what%20Nitish%20has%20done%20as%20are%20those%20outside%20the%20party%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20there%20is%20the%20opportunity%20to%20firm%20up%20a%20truly%20secular%20and%20people-friendly%20common%20agenda%2C%20and%20take%20it%20to%20voters%2C%20especially%20in%20Bihar%2C%20who%20can%20be%20heart-warmingly%20heard%2C%20in%20such%20programmes%20as%20News24%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EMahoul%20Kya%20Hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20express%20their%20disgust%20at%C2%A0%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20latest%20turn-over%2C%20predicting%20a%20rout%20for%20the%20BJP%2FJDU%20coalition%20come%20the%20hustings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20require%20the%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20to%20evidence%20a%20new%20sense%20of%20solidarity%20and%20urgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20continues%20to%20make%20mass%20public%20contact%20and%20necessary%20ideological%20groundwork%2C%20equal%2C%20if%20not%20more%20energetic%20and%20visibly%20credible%2C%20primacy%20needs%20to%20be%20given%20to%20comport%20with%20all%20remaining%20segments%20of%20the%20alliance%20in%20order%20to%20ensure%20a%20real%20electoral%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kharge%20has%20rightly%20cautioned%2C%20were%20the%20coming%C2%A0%20national%20election%20to%20be%20won%20again%20by%20the%20Modi-led%20right-wing%2C%20a%C2%A0%20Putinesque%20order%20may%20well%20come%20to%20be%20a%20reality%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20leads%20to%20the%20conclusion%20that%20should%20the%20Rahul-led%20Yatra%20fail%20to%20become%20a%20cutting-edge%20instrument%20in%20furthering%20the%20electoral%20prospects%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20next%20election%20could%20make%20its%20heroic%20efforts%20redundant%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%C2%A0%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20Congress%20wants%20to%20use%20the%20current%20campaign%20to%20obtain%20numero%20uno%20status%20as%20a%20party%2C%20it%20might%20need%20to%20rethink%20that%20objective%20for%20now%2C%20and%20yield%20to%20the%20more%20pressing%C2%A0%20task%20of%20uncomplainingly%20leaving%20room%20for%20federal%C2%A0%20forces%20who%20might%20be%20better%20placed%2C%20on%20objective%20scrutiny%2C%20to%20show%20successful%20results%20in%20constituencies%20under%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20not%20be%20easy%2C%20given%20that%20the%20Congress%20after%20all%2C%20has%C2%A0%20been%20the%20chief%20ideological%20engine%20and%20nation-builder%20since%20the%20freedom%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20history%20is%20unforgiving%2C%20and%20this%20may%20not%20be%20the%20time%20to%20drive%20home%20that%20record%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20ensuring%20that%20another%20successful%20emancipatory%20result%20is%20realised%20in%20a%20few%20months%20from%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbadri-raina%5C%22%3EBadri%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0taught%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B