my%2Fnews%2Ffy-24-asset-monetisation-falls-short-of-target-at-rs-1-50-trn-official-124020200398_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Refuses%20to%20Hear%20Hemant%20Soren's%20Plea%20Against%20Arrest%20by%20ED%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02115438%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20February%202%20refused%20to%20entertain%20a%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20former%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20challenging%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20approach%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20M.M.%20Sundresh%2C%20and%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%20asked%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20as%20to%20why%20the%20matter%20cannot%20be%20heard%20by%20the%20high%20court%2C%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-former-jharkhand-chief-minister-hemant-soren-arrest-enforcement-directorate-money-laundering-case-248291%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20day%20ago%2C%20a%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20had%20agreed%20to%20list%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20petition%2C%20urgently%2C%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESibal%2C%20at%20the%20apex%20court%20today%2C%20advocated%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20%E2%80%9Csend%20a%20message%E2%80%9D%20in%20such%20matters%20as%20this%20is%20a%20sitting%20chief%20minister%20who%20has%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArrested%20in%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam%20case%2C%20Soren%20had%20to%20relinquish%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20late%20on%20January%2031.%20While%20leaders%20of%20his%20party%2C%20the%20Jharkhand%20Janmukti%20Morcha%2C%20have%20noted%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20arrest%20%E2%80%93%20just%20before%20the%20general%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20and%20called%20it%20a%20brazen%20act%20of%20political%20vendetta%2C%C2%A0Soren%20had%20expressed%20fear%20that%20his%20arrest%20may%20allow%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20impose%20president%E2%80%99s%20rule%20in%20the%20state.%20He%20has%20also%20invoked%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20against%20ED%20officers%20for%20allegedly%20harassing%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%2C%20courts%20are%20open%20to%20everybody.%20Second%2C%20high%20courts%20are%20constitutional%20courts.%20If%20we%20permit%20one%20person%20to%20come%20here%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20allow%20everyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20judge%20also%20said%20that%20the%20court%20had%20refused%20to%20entertain%20Soren%E2%80%99s%20earlier%20plea%20against%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20summons%20to%20him%20on%20the%20same%20plank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoren%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Jharkhand%20high%20court%20challenging%20the%20ED%20arrest.%20When%20he%20filed%20a%20similar%20petition%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20his%20counsel%20Sibal%20undertook%20that%20he%20would%20withdraw%20the%20high%20court%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Sibal%20and%20Singhvi%20attempted%20to%20convince%20the%20court%20that%20it%20has%20concurrent%20jurisdiction%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20noted%20in%20its%20report%20that%20despite%20%E2%80%9Cfervent%20appeals%E2%80%9D%20the%20%E2%80%9Cjudges%20remained%20unswayed%E2%80%9D%20and%20spoke%20in%20favour%20of%20an%20Article%20226%20remedy%20for%20Soren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20also%20did%20not%20stipulate%20a%20timeframe%20for%20the%20high%20court%20even%20upon%20request.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20going%20to%20control%20the%20high%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20S.V.%20Raju%2C%