0PM%20Modi%20won%20a%20second%20term%20-%20Piyush%20Goyal%2C%20who%20was%20then%20the%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20had%20kept%20the%20tax%20slab%20unchanged%2C%20but%20increased%20standard%20deduction%20for%20salaried%20people%20from%20Rs%2040%2C000%20to%20Rs%2050%2C000.%20This%20time%2C%20however%2C%20all%20tax-related%20matters%20have%20been%20left%20untouched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20interim%20Budget%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20had%20also%20hiked%20the%20tax%20deducted%20at%20source%20(TDS)%20limit%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%2040%2C000%20for%20post%20office%20savings%20and%20bank%20deposits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20year%20the%20BJP%20defeated%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%2C%20the%20then%20Finance%20Minister%20P%20Chidambaram%20in%20his%20interim%20Budget%20had%20not%20made%20any%20significant%20changes%20in%20tax%20laws%2C%20but%20tweaked%20indirect%20taxes%20for%20a%20small%20set%20of%20sectors.%20He%20reduced%20excise%20duty%20from%2012%20per%20cent%20to%2010%20per%20cent%20on%20some%20goods%2C%20and%20gave%20relief%20to%20the%20automobile%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20there%20was%20no%20expectation%20of%20a%20change%20in%20tax%20slabs%20in%20this%20interim%20Budget%2C%20there%20was%20speculation%20about%20a%20possible%20increase%20in%20the%20standard%20deduction%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20regime%20does%20not%20allow%20taxpayers%20to%20claim%20deductions%2C%20but%20eases%20the%20tax%20slabs%20for%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20incomes%2C%20while%20the%20old%20regime%20has%20a%20maximum%20tax%20slab%20of%2030%20per%20cent%20from%20a%20lower%20threshold%2C%20but%20also%20allows%20claims%20to%20be%20filed%20for%20deductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20hike%20in%20standard%20deduction%20under%20the%20new%20regime%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20has%20not%20made%20any%20significant%20changes%20in%20taxation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706776020000%2C%22visual%