egulation%20Act%2C%201949%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Said%20On%20RBI%20Restrictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20One%2097%20Communications%20Limited%20(OCL)%2C%20said%20it%20is%20taking%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20steps%26quot%3B%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20RBI's%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCL%2C%20as%20a%20payments%20company%2C%20works%20with%20various%20banks%20(not%20just%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank)%2C%20on%20various%20payments%20products%2C%20the%20fintech%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUpdate%3A%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Limited%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20Paytm%20receives%20RBI%20directions.%20Paytm%20to%20expand%20its%20existing%20relationships%20with%20leading%20third-party%20banks%20to%20distribute%20payments%20and%20financial%20services%20products.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRead%20more%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNsPCOxp6VJ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNsPCOxp6VJ%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FfQjozyR11m%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FfQjozyR11m%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Paytm%20(%40Paytm)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPaytm%2Fstatus%2F1752783857697665354%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2031%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20now%20will%20accelerate%20the%20plans%20and%20completely%20move%20to%20other%20bank%20partners.%20Going%20forward%2C%20OCL%20will%20be%20working%20only%20with%20other%20banks%2C%20and%20not%20with%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Limited.%20The%20next%20phase%20of%20OCL's%20journey%20is%20to%20continue%20to%20expand%20its%20payments%20and%20financial%20services%20business%2C%20only%20in%20partnerships%20with%20other%20banks%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3