0adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20each%20classroom%20door%20is%20brightly%20painted%2C%20the%20entrance%20is%20in%20a%20different%20bright%20colour%2C%20and%20the%20toilet%20doors%20are%20painted%20in%20contrasting%20yet%20vibrant%20colours.%20This%20approach%20ensures%20that%20students%20with%20low%20vision%20can%20readily%20identify%20and%20locate%20important%20elements%2C%20such%20as%20the%20switchboard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmell%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20to%20make%20the%20classrooms%20even%20more%20distinctive%20from%20each%20other%2C%20the%20architect%20decided%20to%20engage%20the%20sense%20of%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20planted%20aromatic%20plants%20at%20entries%2C%20which%20can%20assist%20students%20in%20marking%20and%20identifying%20places.%20These%20elements%20serve%20as%20different%20clues%20incorporated%20into%20our%20design.%20Students%2C%20based%20on%20their%20comfort%20and%20understanding%2C%20use%20these%20clues%20to%20navigate%20the%20building.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20school%20has%20brightly%20coloured%20doors%20to%20help%20the%20students%20with%20partial%20vision%20navigate%20better.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-5-1706623443-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340124%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20school%20has%20brightly%20coloured%20doors%20to%20help%20the%20students%20with%20partial%20vision%20navigate%20better.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInclusive%2C%20sustainable%20and%20a%20haven%20for%20the%20students%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20five%20special%20classrooms%20and%20seven%20classrooms%20with%20individual%20courtyards%20in%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20furniture%20arrangement%20was%20also%20crucial%2C%20and%20the%20shape%20and%20size%20of%20the%20classrooms%20evolved%20based%20on%20how%20students%20would%20sit.%20To%20ensure%20equal%20attention%20from%20the%20teacher%2C%20we%20designed%20a%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99%20shaped%20seating%20arrangement%20where%20each%20student%20is%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20the%20teacher%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20also%20believed%20that%20the%20children%20should%20also%20get%20the%20chance%20to%20learn%20outdoors%2C%20hence%20he%20included%20the%20courtyards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20recognised%20that%20learning%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20only%20happen%20within%20the%20classroom%20but%20extends%20beyond%20its%20walls.%20Considering%20this%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20courtyards%20became%20crucial.%20In%20addition%20to%20their%20educational%20significance%2C%20there%20were%20practical%20reasons%20for%20incorporating%20courtyards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20area%20experiences%20a%20hot%20and%20dry%20climate%2C%20which%20can%20be%20challenging%20for%20students%20with%20low%20vision%20sensitive%20to%20direct%20light.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20we%20ensured%20that%20the%20courtyard%20provides%20filtered%20light%20to%20the%20classrooms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndirect%20light%20was%20a%20significant%20concern%20as%20the%20architect%20aimed%20to%20provide%20a%20comfortable%20learning%20environment%20for%20low-vision%20students%20with%20minimal%20glare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20protect%20the%20low-vision%20students%20from%20direct%20light%20glare%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318714%2Ftamil-nadu-engineer-turns-artist-paints-with-sunlight-vignesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebring%20sunlight%20from%20the%20roof%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20not%20from%20windows%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20haven%20for%20its%20students%2C%20the%20school%20also%20is%20sustainable%20in%20its%20roots.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20be%20very%20frugal%20with%20what%20we%20were%20using.%20We%20used%20only%20locally-sourced%20materials%20such%20as%20Kota%20stone%20and%20planted%20more%20than%201%2C000%20plants%20of%2037%20different%20varieties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20are%20five%20special%20classrooms%20and%20seven%20classrooms%20with%20individual%20courtyards%20in%20the%20school.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-6-1706623850-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl