h%20the%20help%20of%20machines%20in%20the%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20smart%2C%20zero-plastic%20air%20freshener%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22alve%20air%20fresheners%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1706154602428-min-1706189932-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339845%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20air%20fresheners%20are%20eco-friendly%2C%20smart%20and%20made%20of%20floral%20waste%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20freshener%20is%20available%20in%20three%20variants%20for%20homes%2C%20offices%2C%20and%20cars%2C%20offering%20a%20choice%20of%2015%20fragrances.%20Each%20unit%20is%20equipped%20with%20smart%20sensors%20that%20automatically%20activate%20and%20deactivate%20based%20on%20the%20detection%20of%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20presence.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20is%20compatible%20with%20Google%20Assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20freshener%20features%20a%20%3Ca%20rel