dation%20to%20drop%20the%20case%20is%20worth%20every%20plaudit.%20Ranjit%2C%20his%20wife%20Jaganti%2C%20and%20Kiran%20remain%20unfazed.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20think%20of%20Kiran%2C%20every%20fear%20goes%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Ranjit%20in%20the%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRanjit%20simply%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20status%20quo%20and%2C%20because%20of%20that%2C%20showed%20us%20that%20change%20is%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pahuja%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20as%20Kiran%20turned%2018%20by%20the%20time%20the%20editing%20of%20the%20documentary%20film%20was%20completed%2C%20she%20chose%20to%20come%20on%20the%20screen%2C%20not%20wanting%20to%20remain%20hidden.%20She%20wished%20to%20encourage%20other%20survivors%20through%20her%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20film%20would%20also%20connect%20with%20many%20on%20its%20quotient%20of%20resilience%20and%20how%20we%20can%20go%20that%20extra%20mile%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20protecting%20those%20we%20love.%20On%20its%20surface%2C%20it%20may%20feel%20like%20a%20film%20from%20India%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20a%20film%20about%20what%20it%20feels%20to%20be%20a%20human.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20it%20continues%20to%20resonate%2C%20touching%20something%20deep%20inside%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pahuja%20said%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Federal%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20now%20Oscar-nominated%20film%20documentary%20%E2%80%98To%20Kill%20A%20Tiger%E2%80%99%20was%20released%20in%20September%202022%20and%20has%20been%20screened%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310790%2Fpunjab-satwinder-kaur-abb-nahi-social-welfare-society-helps-abandoned-brides-find-justice%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilm%20festivals%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20the%20world%2C%20receiving%20over%2020%20international%20awards%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Best%20Canadian%20Film%20at%20the%20Toronto%20International%20Fil