t%20my%20life%20journey%20is%20being%20taught%20in%20Class%207%20in%20schools%20of%20Xi%E2%80%99an%2C%20where%20I%20started%20my%20entrepreneurship%20journey.%20Although%20I%E2%80%99m%20neither%20a%20graduate%20in%20hotel%20management%20nor%20a%20trained%20actor%2C%20I%20visit%20several%20universities%20in%20China%20to%20teach%20students.%20And%20at%20least%2020%20documentaries%20have%20been%20made%20on%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20if%20you%20are%20passionate%20about%20something%2C%20do%20not%20let%20that%20passion%20die.%20And%20this%20mantra%20helped%20me%20reach%20greater%20heights%20that%20I%20could%20have%20never%20imagined%20coming%20from%20a%20small%20hill%20village%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Dev%20Raturi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706080241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D338745%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20far%20can%20you%20go%20to%20pursue%20your%20passion%3F%20A%20Bruce%20Lee%20fan%2C%20Dev%20Raturi's%20fascination%20with%20martial%20arts%20and%20acting%20took%20him%20from%20Uttarakhand's%20Tehri%20Garhwal%20to%20China.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A352%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338745%2Fdev-raturi-from-uttarakhand-village-becomes-actor-in-chinese-movies%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22From%20Being%20Rejected%20By%207%20Firms%20To%20Becoming%20a%20CEO%20At%2033%3A%20Meet%20Radhika%20Gupta%2C%20Shark%20Tank%20India%E2%80%99s%20New%20Judge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETrigger%20warning%3A%20Mention%20of%20suicide%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERadhika%20Gupta%2C%20the%20managing%20director%20and%20CEO%20of%20Edelweiss%20Asset%20Management%20Limited%2C%20oversees%20assets%20worth%20over%20Rs%201.2%2